  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Hi there big guy!
    nextOption: Squeekalot said you needed help?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Why Yes, I do!


      I can make powerful scrolls to aid our knights
      in the battle.'
    nextOption: They are going to read a story to the goblins?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Not those kind of scrolls silly.


      Scrolls with powers to
      make them harder, faster, better, and stronger.'
    nextOption: How can I help?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'With all the fighting it''s too dangerous to go collect the reeds.


      They
      grow near the water behind the base.'
    nextOption: I know how to collect plants!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Great, bring me back 8 swamp reed and I'll teach you the secrets
      of inscription.
    nextOption: That sounds handy, I'll be right back
